{"entity":{"id":"rec44HYmmM92uyW0g","type":"chapter","slug":"rec44HYmmM92uyW0g","label":"Ps.73","rawId":"rec44HYmmM92uyW0g","book":{"id":"recKXZXO6cJwk2SxO","type":"book","slug":"ps","label":"Psalms","subtitle":"Poetry-Wisdom","count":2461,"description":"150 chapters, 1026 people, 118 places"}},"stats":{"verses":28,"people":2,"places":0,"events":0},"nodes":[{"id":"rec44HYmmM92uyW0g","type":"chapter","group":"focus","label":"Ps.73","slug":"ps_73","score":28},{"id":"recKXZXO6cJwk2SxO","type":"book","group":"book","label":"Psalms","slug":"ps","score":2461},{"id":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"God","slug":"god_1324","score":6},{"id":"recwrDYUkCdyU3t85","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"Asaph (Levite)","slug":"asaph_330","score":1}],"links":[{"source":"rec44HYmmM92uyW0g","target":"recKXZXO6cJwk2SxO","label":"part of"},{"source":"rec44HYmmM92uyW0g","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec44HYmmM92uyW0g","target":"recwrDYUkCdyU3t85","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"recn2WQYCuYv1npan","ref":"Ps.73.1","text":"Truly God is good to Israel, even to such as are of a clean heart."},{"id":"recuRTQGbZbColbfX","ref":"Ps.73.2","text":"But as for me, my feet were almost gone; my steps had well nigh slipped."},{"id":"recxSIt03Ep5okEe3","ref":"Ps.73.3","text":"For I was envious at the foolish, when I saw the prosperity of the wicked."},{"id":"recUOylTYP6mZdmkH","ref":"Ps.73.4","text":"For there are no bands in their death: but their strength is firm."},{"id":"recDMNBIHtRmjqaWS","ref":"Ps.73.5","text":"They are not in trouble as other men; neither are they plagued like other men."},{"id":"recldrvfiM2arm0qL","ref":"Ps.73.6","text":"Therefore pride compasseth them about as a chain; violence covereth them as a garment."},{"id":"recimJf9LNTSuD22N","ref":"Ps.73.7","text":"Their eyes stand out with fatness: they have more than heart could wish."},{"id":"recxGbhUPD4ut9Yta","ref":"Ps.73.8","text":"They are corrupt, and speak wickedly concerning oppression: they speak loftily."}]}
